          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Powering this small muscle car is a 390-cubic-inch V8 engine that generates 325-horsepower and is backed by an automatic transmission. According to the listing on Hemmings, the mileage states 71,062 but is exempt.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
